<div style="font-size: 95px; text-align: center; background: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.5); border-top: 2px solid burlywood; border-bottom: 2px solid burlywood; padding: 5px; border-radius: 0px; text-shadow: 0px 0px 4px #ffffff; letter-spacing: 0.25rem;"><span style="font-family:Rubik Glitch; background:linear-gradient(to right, tan, blanchedalmond, lightsalmon);  -webkit-background-clip:text !important; -webkit-text-fill-color: transparent; text-shadow: floralwhite 0px 0px 8.25px">The Tower of Babel</span></div>


<div style="background-color:rgba(0,0,0,0.35); color: white; margin:1em;font-family:Overpass; padding:5px 10px; text-align:center;">
----
